Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他知道馬可也參加了殲滅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有新情報來了我會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統輔佐就像是做人質一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果樂觀點看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機在大總統睡覺的時候取下他的首級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大佐的傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡還在到處轉悠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳告訴我伊修瓦爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}520先士的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊修瓦爾發生了那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的事情都告訴了我這樣的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師是追求真理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻不知道身邊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐在想達成目的之後的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達成目的之後…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 你恢復原來的身體後想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 想吃溫莉的蘋果派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為腦子裡已經塞滿了恢復原來的身體這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先跟婆婆還有師傅打招呼 告訴他們「回來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 一直受她們照顧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會笑著迎接我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到大家的笑臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然情況很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有好消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的鍊金術無法發動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一個時間 地上似乎也無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個小女孩和斯卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他們能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的鍊金術裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我們不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還沒完全走到死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了？那個豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天一大早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 她說去哪了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整個中央都市？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且完全沒有線索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送就送那種有很多美女照片的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們離開的期間裡 可別偷懶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去品嘗一下西部的著名料理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大後要變強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我離開的期間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹長 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾蔓准尉 還沒有出發嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來向大佐還東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央都市的勤務時間真是短暫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹長是南方司令部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方司令部一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 期待再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來取忘記的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡好像還在中央都市裡晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可得小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且技術好的護衛已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳操勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我跟錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳認為錯了就一槍斃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在允許的範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉可真溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的時候可不要偷懶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該說是興趣增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我很光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為腦子不好 進士官學校可是費了很大的勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您希望 會一直跟您到地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇后也被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 將軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是這種貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在尋找帶著這傢伙的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（妳知道嗎 知道的話請告訴我）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那邊那個異類就放一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 沒有黑白貓的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許已經不在中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 清的鍊丹術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也問問別人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是不想欠大佐人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 說起欠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好前面 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少 500先士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520先士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想糊弄過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這麼精打細算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可成不了大人物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是繼續借著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大佐做了大總統之後再還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰告訴你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克愛中尉 還有伊修瓦爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢就算一直借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓你還給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到那個時候會再問你借零錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說等實行民主制了再還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個也還了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再借一次 定個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我必須活得相當久才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 別讓中尉再擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你送我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精神 瓦涅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 羅伊小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 耶誕節夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了提提精神來玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為病剛好 酒不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一個特別的 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉曼閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位名叫耶誕節夫人的女性從中央都市打來的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別把極密線路的號碼告訴普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還沒被拋棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指名要我這老頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能保護好少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是這副樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算被姚家選上的守護一族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道廉恥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…手臂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蘭芳的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給她介紹機械鎧技師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的好意我們心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不需要進一步的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械鎧技師我們自己會想辦法找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能放著不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人看到了蘭芳的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再把你們的熟人捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了您 孫女的性命保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是個被人感謝的醫生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾克斯醫生 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快點出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒好到把麻煩一直留在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的身體狀況似乎在惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快奪回少主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著長生不老之法回國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著 魔窟的住人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記你的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾克斯醫生 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 裝成醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我這麼個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 父親 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 還精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有重要的事來到附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是瘦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還是老樣子對著屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這週治療了兩個活著的患者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然去救助人命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 我現在以醫生為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道父親自伊修瓦爾以來一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 父親也沒有放棄做醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡作為醫生的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然做得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯咖啡再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂得一塌糊塗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 趁你父親泡咖啡的時候 我們收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有神存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家人一起喝咖啡這點幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是可以擁有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣伊修瓦爾就完全進入國軍的管轄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 金普利少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視等價交換 實現了超越想像的鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況寫成文書後提交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭還給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這樣知道賢者之石所在的只有你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被釋放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的命令嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你殺了五個士官卻沒被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使了什麼招？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是我的人望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別笑死人了 炸彈狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然釋放你這種發狂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長時間受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的玩具 送給你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你出獄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你們的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為人手不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說會給我工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得馬可醫生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作了賢者之石的研究者吧 我記得他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個馬可也許
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有完全確定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看門的合成獸少了一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可是擅長生物鍊成的鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更麻煩的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能和伊修瓦爾人斯卡一起逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為實行了伊修瓦爾殲滅戰的紅蓮之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我手下漏掉的伊修瓦爾人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可原諒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現斯卡殺死也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馬可要帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為了這點事把我叫出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抓住了馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以儆效尤 毀掉一座城市給他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會做骯髒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來能用上這久違的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毀滅一個城市 那個或許不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？又用了伊修瓦爾人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬克醫生的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直研究著石頭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼放我走？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那個叫金普利的鍊金術師之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長留下的研究書裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我無法理解的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究書？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長臨死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這個國家的鍊金術很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點 應該有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是優秀的鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的鍊金術 很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 那個女孩回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生 您沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴增加了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是製作賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助伊修瓦爾殲滅戰的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之石是？長生不老的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可先生 你知道石頭的製作方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做的？請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要追求那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只破壞了臉的表面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他止血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉還是破壞得看不出是你比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（不要緊嗎 馬可先生）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我藏了兄長的研究書之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏著的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和微笑一同出現
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的火苗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨在錯綜的中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第32話 大總統的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道反而會比較幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:27.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因為我猶豫不決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:31.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}輕微的顫抖著  control過了還在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太陽也好  運氣（月亮）也罷  完全與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「只有硬上了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:39.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我這樣勸說自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:45.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情況很糟糕  臨陣逃脫又沒毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:49.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}雖然前途未卜  也只能靠膽量獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:52.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}壓制著衝動  尋找敵我之間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是勝利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能嘗下勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下滿腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二擇其一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操縱命運的輪盤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:15.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}絕好的黃金時間  親自把握機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:19.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}擺出一副撲克臉  設下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:24.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敵人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無盡的pressure game  跨越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:35.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}為了跨越榮耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:39.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:44.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底捨不得放棄哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:45.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:48.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}談話直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牽手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:56.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就這樣明天後天也一直這樣形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:23:00.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看著街上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:06.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人是無法找到溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:11.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道愛原來可以如此堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:17.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在與你相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:28.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:33.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為一個人無法入睡  也無法做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:39.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安無法到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是沒有星星的夜晚也要繼續將其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的話能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:49.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一個人無法走過的道路  如果是兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼著歌走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:56.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福


